spec_data.Name: ansible-openstack-modules
spec_data.Description:
Unofficial Ansible modules for managing and deployment of OpenStack. Contains
all the necesary Neutron networking modules and also some Cinder, Glance,
Keystone and Nova modules missing in the official modules.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:28:39 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Unofficial Ansible modules for managing Openstack
